query:
UPDATE reprezentanti 
        SET 
            nume = $2,
            prenume = $3,
            cnp = $4,
            tip_act_identitate = $5,
            serie_act_identitate = $6,
            numar_act_identitate = $7,
            calitate = $8,
            telefon = $9,
            email = $10,
            data_nasterii = $11,
            adresa_domiciliu = $12,
            updated_at = NOW()
        WHERE uuid = $1
